nd America's global economic standing.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAntitrust law -- United States. 0aAntitrust lawzUnited States. 0aTelecommunication -- Law and legislation -- United States. 0aTelecommunicationxLaw and legislationzUnited States. 7aLAW / Business & Financial.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030016737540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300167375423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300167375/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles